==Usage==
This template is used to mark certain sentences so that they can be viewed in their native language.

For example:

<code><nowiki>{{lang|ja|艦これ}}</nowiki></code>

Will render the word into its native language like this:

{{lang|ja|艦これ}}<includeonly>
